My skincare regime has always been of the outmost importance and for that I am obsessed with the @oriflameindia Optimals Range. #OptimalsSkincare #BeautyBySweden #InspiredByNature #PoweredByScience #EvenOutSkin

#TheAIAffair with @mgmotorin is new to you but our love for their machines goes back to their first ever launch in India so when we heard of the #MGAstor coming to town, we had to take it out for a spin! India’s First Personal AI Assistant Car which I have to admit is an AMAZING experience from the comfort, to the interiors, our absolute favourite the sunroof and oh our new friend in town, the Astor robot! Give it a ride and you'll know! #MGMotor #mgmotorindia
